{"type": "article", "id": 12173, "title": "Grovemade 木制手表", "description": "", "date": "2015-07-16T10:29:13Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 28, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606060002208HIWAFYNvjkworOZ.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t来自波特兰的设计品牌 Grovemade 推出的这一款手表采用木制材料，他们把手表上的数字和指针全部抽走，只剩下十二个小圈圈，红色显示小时，白色则显示分钟。预定时，你可以选择不同形状的表盘，并且有胡桃木和枫木两种材质可选，而表带也有真皮和硅胶两种不同材质，可以按照个人喜好搭配在一起。手表售价 239 美元，<a href=\"http://grovemade.com/collections/wood-watch\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里</a>可以购买。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140012iLOMepKolEfCG6xk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.18351064\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261400137Pe4zCOV0yDcQR8f.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67407407\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140013Dn9yhl1U2iCctWGF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.65185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261400147089fleuKd4UHaOk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66018519\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140014Yrwc95bqZSKO0BeP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67222222\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n\n"}